{
  "stem": "3928.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They checked all of his SS, different SS outposts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I was able to find out a lot of information, you know, really-- what was like troop movements.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they called back troops, you know, from one front to another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Actually, what Hitler wanted, he wanted to make Hungary as a fighting point, so they let ruin Hungary instead of Austria or Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whatever he want, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's what he want-- wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he pulled all the forces, you know, one time, and put them in the Hungarian border, but the Russian's forces were so tremendous really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the German soldiers at that time, they were lack of everything from-- from lack of a food, to lack of spirit, and lack of ammunition and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, they weren't a fighting force anymore, you know, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were nothing, just a scratch force, and-- which was fortunate, you know, at the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, that's they way they were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I honestly feel this way, that the majority of the killings, they weren't done by the Germans itself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They may ordered by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't question this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I don't question just they may supervise it, but the actual killing was done by the Polish SS, by the Croatian SS, by the Baltic SS, and the Hungarian arrowheads.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were actually the lord's high executioners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, after the war, quite a few were put in trial in Hungary, and they were executed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You know why.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But for-- you know, too many escaped, you know, really, who actually was responsible for the killing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were-- it wasn't hesitant, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If somebody was any doubt, just shoot him.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
